-- Equinox Increases Scale of Study Into Lumwana Copper Project in Zambia
-- B y   A n d r e w   H o b b s
-- 2011-02-03T03:19:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-03/equinox-increases-scale-of-study-into-lumwana-copper-project-in-zambia.html
  Equinox Minerals Ltd . increased the
scale of its study into its Lumwana copper project, enlarging
the projected plant to support an operation that could process
45 million metric tons of ore annually from an initial estimate
of 20 million tons a year. The study is due to be completed in
the second quarter this year, the company said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Hobbs at 
 ahobbs4@bloomberg.net  